A #healthcareworker in the US suffered an allergic reaction after receiving Pfizer's Covid-19 vaccine.

#PfizerBioNTech #Allergic  #US @US_FDA @CDCgov
date: US healthcare worker suffers allergic reaction to Pfizer vaxThe worker was among the healthcare workers being vaccinated at Bartlett Regional Hospital in Juneau in the US state of Alaska on Tuesday.dtnext.in
